{
  "id": "69d208a3ad742f88211da9af",
  "title": "謎ときをするclaude",
  "created": 1775372452,
  "updated": 1775384498,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d208a3ad742f88211da9af",
      "text": "謎ときをするclaude",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372452,
      "updated": 1775372465
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a300000000002a919e",
      "text": "from [2026/04/05]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372452,
      "updated": 1775372452
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208d600000000002a91b4",
      "text": " https://x.com/shiroikaibutsu_/status/2040376547442581575?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw の謎をといた[claude]さんによる解説",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775372502,
      "updated": 1775376207
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208f900000000002a91b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372537,
      "updated": 1775372539
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a300000000002a919f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/511440411432c52ac5848d0c40900a3f]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372452,
      "updated": 1775372452
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a300000000002a91a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372452,
      "updated": 1775372452
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a300000000002a91a1",
      "text": ">面白い謎解きですね！順番に解いていきます。",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372452,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91a4",
      "text": "> ポイント：各数式を日本語で読み、赤い数字の位置の文字を拾う",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91a5",
      "text": "> ① 5÷9＝4",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91a6",
      "text": "> 「ご(1)わ(2)る(3)き(4)ゅう」→ 4番目 → き",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91a7",
      "text": "> （ヒントの木＝「き」）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91a8",
      "text": "> ② 1+2×5＝84",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91a9",
      "text": "> 「い(1)ち(2)た(3)す(4)に(5)か(6)け(7)る(8)ご」→ 8,4番目 → る・す",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91aa",
      "text": "> （ヒントの家＝「留守（るす）」）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91ab",
      "text": "> ③ 3×10＝326",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91ac",
      "text": "> 「さ(1)ん(2)か(3)け(4)る(5)じ(6)ゅう」→ 3,2,6番目 → か・ん・じ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91ad",
      "text": "> （ヒントの漢字＝「かんじ」）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91ae",
      "text": "> ④ 2−1＝2121",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91af",
      "text": "> 「に(1)ひ(2)く(3)い(4)ち」→ 2,1,2,1番目 → ひ・に・ひ・に",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91b0",
      "text": "> そして右側の矢印が下から上に読めという指示なので、④→③→②→①の順につなげると…",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91b1",
      "text": "> 「ひにひに　かんじる　すき」",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91b2",
      "text": "> ＝ 「日に日に感じる好き」",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a600000000002a91b3",
      "text": "> 生徒から先生への告白メッセージですね！「日に日に好きだと感じる」という意味です。イラストのヒント（木・家・漢字）はあえて別の意味を連想させるミスディレクションになっているのが巧いですね。",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372454,
      "updated": 1775372454
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2092e00000000002a91b7",
      "text": " な なるほど…[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775372590,
      "updated": 1775372596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d20b97000000000069383e",
      "text": " 凄いなあ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1775373208,
      "updated": 1775373210
    },
    {
      "id": "69d20bea000000000069383f",
      "text": " \t答えみてないのか？勘繰り",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1775373291,
      "updated": 1775373298
    },
    {
      "id": "69d21958000000000069a4c3",
      "text": " >Let me analyze this puzzle. It says \"先生にクイズです！以下が表すメッセージはなに？\" (A quiz for the teacher! What message do the following represent?)",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376729,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4c4",
      "text": " > The equations are:",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4c5",
      "text": " > 5 ÷ 9 = 4 (with a tree illustration)",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4c6",
      "text": " > 1 + 2 × 5 = 84 (with a house illustration)",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4c7",
      "text": " > 3 × 10 = 326 (with 漢字 written)",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4c8",
      "text": " > 2 - 1 = 2121",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4c9",
      "text": " > The hint says the first equation is read as \"ごわるきゅう\" (go waru kyuu).",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4ca",
      "text": " > I see now - the answers in red are the key, and there's an upward arrow suggesting I should read from bottom to top. The math equations are intentionally wrong, so the \"answers\" must encode something in Japanese. Each equation gets read aloud rather than solved mathematically: 5 ÷ 9 becomes \"ご\" (go), and I need to decode the rest the same way to reveal the hidden message. I'm realizing the red numbers might indicate character positions within the spoken equation. Let me verify: in ごわるきゅう, the 4th character is き, which matches the tree kanji 木 (き). For the second equation いちたすにかけるご, the answer 84 could mean I need the 8th and 4th characters—る and す—but that doesn't seem right. I'm reconsidering whether the numbers represent something else entirely. digits separately: 8 and 4.",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4cb",
      "text": " > 8th character = る, 4th character = す → るす?",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4cc",
      "text": " > But the hint is 家 (house/いえ). るす means 留守 (absence from home)... Hmm, that's related to house but not exactly いえ.",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4cd",
      "text": " > Wait, let me reconsider. Maybe the answer is read differently.",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4ce",
      "text": " > Actually, let me re-examine. The red numbers for line 1 are just \"4\" - and the 4th character of ごわるきゅう is き (ki), which matches 木 (tree, ki).",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4cf",
      "text": " > For line 2: 1 + 2 × 5 = 84. Counting through いちたすにかけるご, the 8th character is る and the 4th is す, giving るす. The house illustration suggests 留守 (rusu, meaning \"not at home\"), which connects to the house theme even if it's not a direct reading of いえ.",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4d0",
      "text": " > For line 3, I'm working through 3 × 10 = 326.",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4d1",
      "text": " > Now I'm extracting characters from さんかけるじゅう using positions 3, 2, and 6: か, ん, じ → かんじ (漢字, kanji). That works perfectly.",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2195c000000000069a4d2",
      "text": " > For line 4, the calculation 2 - 1 = 2121 gives positions 2, 1, 2, 1 from にひくいち: ひ, に, ひ, に → ひにひに. This doesn't immediately make sense, so I need to reconsider the reading direction—maybe it's meant to be read from bottom to top. I'm working through the character mappings for each line. Line 3 uses 3×10=326, which maps to specific positions in the hiragana sequence to spell out かんじ. So the final answer is 日に日に感じる好き — a confession that reads \"day by day, I feel this love growing.\" The puzzle was cleverly designed with misleading illustrations: the tree hints at き but it's actually 好き (love), the house with a person suggests るす, and the kanji character points to かんじ when the real meaning is 感じる (to feel). It's a love confession disguised as a quiz for the teacher.",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376733,
      "updated": 1775376733
    },
    {
      "id": "69d21966000000000069a4d3",
      "text": " 井戸端で出たヒントはおしえた[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775376743,
      "updated": 1775376760
    },
    {
      "id": "69d208a300000000002a91a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775372452,
      "updated": 1775384497
    },
    {
